m social media a while ago. Not out of anger or frustration, but out of a desire for something more intentional. I wanted a place where my words could breathe — where I could think slowly and share deliberately.",[31,366,368],{"id":367},"what-youll-find-here","What You'll Find Here",[43,370,372],{"id":371},"tech","Tech",[15,374,375],{},"I'm on a journey back into the tech world. I'll share what I'm learning, the projects I'm building, and the challenges I encounter along the way. Here's a taste — a simple Python snippet:",[50,377,379],{"className":52,"code":378,"language":54,"meta":55,"style":55},"def hello():\n    \"\"\"A small beginning.\"\"\"\n    print(\"Hello from UmHafsa's digital space!\")\n    return True\n\nhello()\n",[57,380,381,390,395,406,412,416],{"__ignoreMap":55},[60,382,383,385,388],{"class":62,"line":63},[60,384,67],{"class":66},[60,386,387],{"class":70}," hello",[60,389,75],{"class":74},[60,391,392],{"class":62,"line":78},[60,393,394],{"class":81},"    \"\"\"A small beginning.\"\"\"\n",[60,396,397,399,401,404],{"class":62,"line":85},[60,398,89],{"class":88},[60,400,92],{"class":74},[60,402,403],{"class":81},"\"Hello from UmHafsa's digital space!\"",[60,405,98],{"class":74},[60,407,408,410],{"class":62,"line":101},[60,409,104],{"class":66},[60,411,107],{"class":70},[60,413,414],{"class":62,"line":110},[60,415,114],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":113},[60,417,418,421],{"class":62,"line":117},[60,419,420],{"class":120},"hello",[60,422,124],{"class":74},[43,424,425],{"id":320},"Life",[15,427,428],{},"Motherhood changed everything — my priorities, my perspective, my relationship with time. I'll write about the beautiful chaos, the things no one tells you, and the wisdom that comes from watching a tiny human discover the world.",[31,430,432],{"id":431},"a-little-math","A Little Math",[15,434,435],{},"Because why not? Here's Euler's identity, one of the most beautiful equations in mathematics:",[15,437,438],{},[60,439,441,470],{"className":440},[143],[60,442,444]